#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/materials/properties/ramps.rst:47
msgid "Shader"
msgstr "着色器"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/materials/properties/ramps.rst:47
msgid ""
"The value as delivered by the material's shader (*Lambert*, *Cook-Torrance*) "
"defines the color. Here the amount of light does not matter for color, only the "
"direction of the light."
msgstr ""
"与材质的着色器(*兰伯特* 、 *库克 托伦斯*)一样，该值用于定义颜色，这种情况下，只有"
"光线的方向影响颜色，光线的数量不影响。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/materials/properties/ramps.rst:50
msgid "Energy"
msgstr "能量"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/materials/properties/ramps.rst:50
msgid ""
"As *Shader*, now also lamp energy, color, and distance are taken into account. "
"This makes the material change color when more light shines on it."
msgstr ""
"与 *着色器* 一样，不过现在将光源能量、颜色和距离考虑在内。这使得当增加照射到材质"
"表面的光线时，材质颜色随之发生变化。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/materials/properties/ramps.rst:53
msgid "Normal"
msgstr "法线"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/materials/properties/ramps.rst:53
msgid ""
"The surface normal, relative to the camera, is used for the *Ramp Shader*. This "
"is possible with a texture as well, but added for convenience."
msgstr ""
"将相对相机的表面法向用于 *渐变着色器* 。这也可以使用贴图实现，不过为了方便还是加"
"入了该选项。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/materials/properties/ramps.rst:57
msgid "Result"
msgstr "渲染结果"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/materials/properties/ramps.rst:56
msgid ""
"While all three previous options work per lamp, this option only works after "
"shading calculations. This allows full control over the entire shading, "
"including 'Toon' style results. Using alpha values here is most useful for "
"tweaking a finishing touch to a material."
msgstr ""
"前面3个选项对每个光源都起作用，但这个选项只有在着色计算结束之后才发挥作用。这样可"
"以完全掌控整体着色，包括 '卡通' 风格的渲染结果。在这里使用alpha值，可以对材质起到"
"画龙点睛的作用。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/materials/properties/ramps.rst:60
